title: My Tesla Crushed My Finger - Seriously

media:group.media:title: My Tesla Crushed My Finger - Seriously
media:group.media:description:
I found myself in an unusual situation where I wanted to manually close the boot, slowly to check the glass would clear the treadmill (for use as a desk!) I’d just loaded up. The trouble is, if you’ve got your fingers over the edge when it’s just about to close something pretty terrifying happens!
